      <event start="T62-429" end="T64-13">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T64-13" end="T64-683">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T66-663" end="T68-523">To dva tedna poj že? </event>
      <event start="T68-523" end="T70-555">Tud dva tedna mine do ... </event>
      <event start="T72-728" end="T21">A, </event>
      <event start="T21" end="T73-684">okej, okej. </event>
      <event start="T86-91" end="T87-482">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T91-518" end="T92-19">Joj. </event>
      <event start="T96-169" end="T97-651">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T98-611" end="T99-321">Žena, plis. </event>
      <event start="T110-148" end="T110-796">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T116-022" end="T116-701">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T119-848" end="T33">J@@, </event>
      <event start="T33" end="T121-399">v šolo? </event>
      <event start="T121-743" end="T122-33">Aaa! </event>
      <event start="T122-954" end="T123-733">Ne! </event>
      <event start="T124-326" end="T125-355">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T126-379" end="T34">Obvij@sli, da se ne oglasi, </event>
      <event start="T34" end="T129-006">zakaj bi se oglasil? </event>
      <event start="T132-816" end="T134-651">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T136-419" end="T137-711">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T141-27" end="T141-574">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T144-181" end="T147-598">A to tko, tip, k stalno dela v domu al tko kr en? </event>
      <event start="T148-747" end="T41">Po() blage, </event>
      <event start="T41" end="T149-748">okej. </event>
      <event start="T155-191" end="T44">A, </event>
      <event start="T44" end="T156-201">okej okej. </event>
      <event start="T165-739" end="T166-397">Ja ... </event>
      <event start="T166-397" end="T168-172">Ne, nisi. </event>
      <event start="T170-446" end="T172-294">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T172-294" end="T172-975">Kok bed. </event>
      <event start="T175-459" end="T176-099">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T176-099" end="T176-837">Varkota. </event>
      <event start="T178-246" end="T179-388">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T181-035" end="T181-465">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T184-731" end="T186-012">Pridejo. </event>
      <event start="T186-528" end="T188-490">Ja sam, a </event>
      <event start="T188-490" end="T56">an() če ni dežurna, </event>
      <event start="T56" end="T191-673">a ni to fora, da bi on mogu bit skos tam? </event>
      <event start="T191-673" end="T193-18">Ne da pride poj. </event>
      <event start="T193-18" end="T194-119">Če je dežuren. </event>
      <event start="T196-546" end="T57">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T58">ja. </event>
      <event start="T58" end="T59">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T59" end="T199-602">vatever. </event>
      <event start="T203-189" end="T204-418">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T205-539" end="T61">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T61" end="T207-395">Ou. </event>
      <event start="T213-717" end="T62">"Mene tud boli, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T216-135">jz bi tud." </event>
      <event start="T217-133" end="T217-874">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T223-453" end="T226-456">To se vedno pol morš prpravt poj na na pet ur plus. </event>
      <event start="T228-28" end="T229-744">Ooo! </event>
      <event start="T229-744" end="T231-239">Nobenga? </event>
      <event start="T236-858" end="T238-04">Ona sta sama not zdela? </event>
      <event start="T238-718" end="T239-937">Ooo bed. </event>
      <event start="T245-306" end="T245-627">Uh! </event>
      <event start="T251-425" end="T251-81">Kom()? </event>
      <event start="T252-61" end="T77">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T77" end="T253-806">okej okej. </event>
      <event start="T259-040" end="T259-687">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T262-41" end="T80">Obvijusli, </event>
      <event start="T80" end="T81">veš, </event>
      <event start="T81" end="T264-081">zih ni dobr naredu, </event>
      <event start="T264-081" end="T264-524">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T267-072" end="T268-106">O, moj bog! </event>
      <event start="T269-924" end="T270-891">Oh! </event>
      <event start="T270-891" end="T272-076">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T272-943" end="T274-68">Všeč mi je, da je šov to teb razlagat, pač. </event>
      <event start="T276-294" end="T277-655">Z medicinsko sestro? </event>
      <event start="T277-971" end="T279-396">Zih mata afero. </event>
      <event start="T279-396" end="T281-373">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T281-959" end="T84">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T84" end="T282-742">okej. </event>
      <event start="T287-756" end="T289-244">On je tebe vprašal? </event>
      <event start="T289-244" end="T290-091">Dober. </event>
      <event start="T295-154" end="T299-473">A pa to je za plačat za inekcije ... al to ti krije z ...? </event>
      <event start="T300-974" end="T89">Okej okej. </event>
      <event start="T89" end="T90">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T90" end="T303-085">jz to vem. </event>
      <event start="T305-162" end="T305-915">Nn! </event>
      <event start="T306-571" end="T93">Ooo </event>
      <event start="T93" end="T94">najebala, </event>
      <event start="T94" end="T309-311">najebala. </event>
      <event start="T311-963" end="T95">Ja oh, </event>
      <event start="T95" end="T96">itak, </event>
      <event start="T96" end="T313-884">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T315-44" end="T316-116">M? </event>
      <event start="T317-435" end="T99">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T99" end="T319-119">Jebote. </event>
      <event start="T321-199" end="T322-52">A preh te sploh ni na dotik? </event>
      <event start="T322-981" end="T323-534">Oh. </event>
      <event start="T323-534" end="T325-118">Bed. </event>
      <event start="T325-118" end="T100">Men je to, </event>
      <event start="T100" end="T101">enkat sem šla k te, v osnovno šolo k zobarci, </event>
      <event start="T101" end="T328-549">k isto. </event>
      <event start="T328-549" end="T329-759">Me najb@l me je zob bolel. </event>
      <event start="T329-759" end="T102">In sem šla k njej, </event>
      <event start="T102" end="T332-27">k je pač isto dežurna bla. </event>
      <event start="T332-27" end="T103">In eee ona tko pride tko: </event>
      <event start="T103" end="T104">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T104" end="T335-944">ti maš gnoj pod zobom." </event>
      <event start="T335-944" end="T105">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T105" end="T106">"Vat du ju ... </event>
      <event start="T106" end="T337-6">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T337-6" end="T339-388">vat d fak du ju min?" [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T339-388" end="T341-421">In ona men zvrtala not lukno. </event>
      <event start="T341-938" end="T342-586">V zob. </event>
      <event start="T342-876" end="T343-879">Da je šu gnoj ven. </event>
      <event start="T343-879" end="T344-837">Takat sem bla še ful m@jhna, </event>
      <event start="T344-837" end="T107">to ni blo zdej, </event>
      <event start="T107" end="T346-788">ampak da je šu gnoj ven. </event>
      <event start="T346-788" end="T348-985">In mene pač ona pusti najd@l cajta. </event>
      <event start="T348-985" end="T350-281">Pridem nazaj ... </event>
      <event start="T350-281" end="T108">al ... ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T108" end="T109">ne vem, kako je že blo, </event>
      <event start="T109" end="T353-453">skratka, spet sem rabla k njej. </event>
      <event start="T353-453" end="T110">In mi ga je ona eem </event>
      <event start="T110" end="T111">pač bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T111" end="T112">"Zdej ga bova pa spule," </event>
      <event start="T112" end="T357-322">k je pač bil mlečen. </event>
      <event start="T357-322" end="T113">Hvala bogu, </event>
      <event start="T113" end="T114">ampak bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T114" end="T359-344">"Zdej ga bova spule." </event>
      <event start="T359-344" end="T360-567">K m() pač ... mrtu je. </event>
      <event start="T361-072" end="T115">[zvok] In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T115" end="T362-368">"Okej." </event>
      <event start="T362-368" end="T116">Ona mi ga pul </event>
      <event start="T116" end="T364-063">in ne gre ven. </event>
      <event start="T364-063" end="T367-660">In se ji tip eee zdrobi v moji dlesni. </event>
      <event start="T367-660" end="T117">In ni mogla sv() cevga sploh dat ven </event>
      <event start="T117" end="T118">in sem mela že tko, </event>
      <event start="T118" end="T119">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T119" end="T373-607">tri leta poj tko noter koščke. </event>
      <event start="T373-607" end="T375-732">Pač pa še z() pa še pa še zadi je blo, </event>
      <event start="T375-732" end="T377-471">k mi ni ful ccc cajta zrasu. </event>
      <event start="T377-471" end="T120">In naenkrat se sam zbudim, </event>
      <event start="T120" end="T379-194">sam tko: </event>
      <event start="T379-194" end="T121">"Hm, </event>
      <event start="T121" end="T122">ni več koščkov, </event>
      <event start="T122" end="T381-499">ajm don." </event>
      <event start="T381-499" end="T383-136">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T386-038" end="T386-391">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T387-004" end="T124">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T124" end="T388-258">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T389-955" end="T125">Najb@l trdi, </event>
      <event start="T125" end="T392-542">mi jih je s cimra prnesla. </event>
      <event start="T392-853" end="T393-422">Najb@l trdi. </event>
      <event start="T396-656" end="T397-651">Jabolčni zih. </event>
      <event start="T398-313" end="T399-251">Ooh. </event>
      <event start="T401-724" end="T403-382">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T406-256" end="T406-695">Oh! </event>
      <event start="T408-912" end="T410-282">Jz bi jokala. </event>
      <event start="T411-379" end="T412-146">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T414-576" end="T416-382">Dets ... trometik. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T416-382" end="T417-141">Kok si bla stara? </event>
      <event start="T418-983" end="T132">Zobna miška. </event>
      <event start="T132" end="T421-842">Ja! [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T421-842" end="T133">Fak, </event>
      <event start="T133" end="T134">jz sm, </event>
      <event start="T134" end="T425-449">jz sem vedno tko pisala pisma zobni miški. </event>
      <event start="T425-449" end="T135">Mi smo mel miško, </event>
      <event start="T135" end="T426-767">ne vilo. </event>
      <event start="T426-767" end="T428-489">Zo() zobna miška. </event>
      <event start="T428-489" end="T137">In sem, vedno sem jo tko najb@l spraševala vprašanja </event>
      <event start="T137" end="T434-774">in pol si prav sam tko predstavlam moja starša, k sta tko u sred noči tm u cimru tko: </event>
      <event start="T434-774" end="T138">"Kaj nej ji odgovoriva, </event>
      <event start="T138" end="T437-338">k@ko nej ji to razloživa? </event>
      <event start="T437-338" end="T139">Ne vem, kaj, </event>
      <event start="T139" end="T439-4">ne vem, kaj." </event>
      <event start="T439-4" end="T140">In zadnč mi tko mami kaže </event>
      <event start="T140" end="T442-816">in ma tko vse moje zobe. </event>
      <event start="T442-816" end="T443-761">Mi jih pokaže. </event>
      <event start="T443-761" end="T141">Vse, </event>
      <event start="T141" end="T142">no, </event>
      <event start="T142" end="T444-835">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T444-835" end="T446-35">velik. </event>
      <event start="T446-35" end="T143">Oh! </event>
      <event start="T143" end="T447-758">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T447-758" end="T449-358">ampak enkrat sem jo vprašala. </event>
      <event start="T449-358" end="T451-399">Po moje je bla tud moja. </event>
      <event start="T451-399" end="T144">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T144" end="T453-848">sej to je tko ful ime za miš. </event>
      <event start="T453-848" end="T145">Zobno miš, </event>
      <event start="T145" end="T454-924">aj ges. </event>
      <event start="T455-504" end="T146">Ama bla sem tko: </event>
      <event start="T146" end="T147">"Mami, </event>
      <event start="T147" end="T458-773">zakaj maš to spravlen?" [glas] </event>
      <event start="T458-773" end="T459-634">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T464-405" end="T464-961">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T465-456" end="T465-978">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T467-727" end="T468-169">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T469-669" end="T470-094">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T472-382" end="T151">Eeh! </event>
      <event start="T151" end="T473-828">Nou! </event>
      <event start="T476-836" end="T477-975">To s dober n@rdila. </event>
      <event start="T478-861" end="T155">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T155" end="T481-750">to sem bla jst najb@l konvinst, da so parklni ril. </event>
      <event start="T481-750" end="T156">K pač, mi smo bli vedno, </event>
      <event start="T156" end="T157">parklni so vedno pršli k nam, </event>
      <event start="T157" end="T485-59">k eee k mam. </event>
      <event start="T485-919" end="T158">A ne, </event>
      <event start="T158" end="T487-563">in takrt je še moj stric živel pr mam. </event>
      <event start="T488-068" end="T159">In jz sem bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T159" end="T160">"Vem, da niso par()," </event>
      <event start="T160" end="T161">prov rekla sem mojim staršem pa moju stricu pa mam: </event>
      <event start="T161" end="T162">"Vem, da parklni niso ril, </event>
      <event start="T162" end="T163">ker vedno, k pride parkl sem, moj stric gre, </event>
      <event start="T163" end="T497-552">a n." </event>
      <event start="T497-552" end="T164">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T164" end="T165">"Ha ha, </event>
      <event start="T165" end="T499-133">jz sem vas vse pogruntala." </event>
      <event start="T499-133" end="T501-074">Naslednje leto ... </event>
      <event start="T501-074" end="T166">pride parkl, </event>
      <event start="T166" end="T167">a moj stric je olso tm, </event>
      <event start="T167" end="T168">k je enmu prjatlu reku, če se [smeh] lahko obleče, </event>
      <event start="T168" end="T507-890">glih zard tega, [smeh] k sem jz rekla. </event>
      <event start="T507-890" end="T169">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T169" end="T509-45">sam aj vas skerd šitles. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T509-45" end="T510-110">Jz sem tm v kotu tko sedela na unmu, </event>
      <event start="T510-110" end="T170">okrogu stol je bil, </event>
      <event start="T170" end="T171">prov spovnem se, </event>
      <event start="T171" end="T172">jz se tko tresem </event>
      <event start="T172" end="T514-796">in tko mol@m tko: </event>
      <event start="T514-796" end="T173">"O moj bog. </event>
      <event start="T173" end="T516-770">Pros@m!" </event>
      <event start="T516-770" end="T518-18">Fotr se mi v glavo smeje. </event>
      <event start="T518-18" end="T521-511">Enkrat, enkrat je pustu fakin ketno parkl. </event>
      <event start="T521-511" end="T522-344">Jz sem bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T522-344" end="T175">"No, </event>
      <event start="T175" end="T523-515">dis sov skeri." [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T525-146" end="T527-363">Ne štekam hajpa glede parklnov. </event>
      <event start="T531-865" end="T534-124">Ampak mene je blo sam strah pač. </event>
      <event start="T534-124" end="T179">To to dela en mesec. </event>
      <event start="T179" end="T180">In tko: </event>
      <event start="T180" end="T537-354">"Božiček te gleda." </event>
      <event start="T537-354" end="T538-473">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T538-473" end="T181">Tko: </event>
      <event start="T181" end="T182">"Vov." </event>
      <event start="T182" end="T539-395">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T540-574" end="T540-915">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T544-827" end="T545-335">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T546-929" end="T547-643">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T549-100" end="T550-562">Se obleč u parkla? </event>
      <event start="T555-695" end="T556-259">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T561-038" end="T191">Šit, </event>
      <event start="T191" end="T563-108">ampak to j tud foter enkrat nam naredu, </event>
      <event start="T563-108" end="T564-788">prov v stanovanje je pršov. </event>
      <event start="T564-788" end="T193">In poj in poj je bla mami tko: </event>
      <event start="T193" end="T567-425">"Aljaž, Aljaž!" </event>
      <event start="T567-425" end="T194">In on tko prteče nazaj not tko: </event>
      <event start="T194" end="T195">"Kaj je blo, </event>
      <event start="T195" end="T196">kaj je blo? </event>
      <event start="T196" end="T570-627">Bil sem u kleti." </event>
      <event start="T570-627" end="T572-134">[glas] To sem jz čist pozabla, </event>
      <event start="T572-134" end="T573-903">to si me zdej to spov@nla si me. </event>
      <event start="T573-903" end="T575-202">Jz sem bla so skerd. </event>
      <event start="T576-939" end="T197">O, </event>
      <event start="T197" end="T577-582">jokala? </event>
      <event start="T578-488" end="T580-031">No. </event>
      <event start="T583-609" end="T199">O ne, </event>
      <event start="T199" end="T584-810">ne, </event>
      <event start="T584-810" end="T200">ne, </event>
      <event start="T200" end="T585-545">aj dont get det. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T586-291" end="T587-118">Dets sov skeri. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T588-089" end="T201">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T201" end="T589-458">jz se jz se jz se bi zdej cmerala, </event>
      <event start="T589-458" end="T590-495">če bi šla. </event>
      <event start="T590-495" end="T591-899">Ar ju kiding k k ... [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T591-899" end="T202">On on bi me vžgov, </event>
