      <event start="T1092-922" end="T1094-114">vedno sem bla pol ... </event>
      <event start="T1095-438" end="T1096-274">Bela. </event>
      <event start="T1096-905" end="T1097-385">Bela. </event>
      <event start="T1098-214" end="T1099-852">Pa kdo ne bi hotu bit Bela? </event>
      <event start="T1101-610" end="T1102-178">Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1102-178" end="T1103-066">O maj gad. </event>
      <event start="T1103-066" end="T348">K je sam zdela na unmu stolu </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T349">in bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T350">"Kje je Edvard, </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T1106-642">aj mis im." </event>
      <event start="T1106-642" end="T1107-612">Dats so mi. </event>
      <event start="T1107-612" end="T1108-628">Jz se čist strinjam. </event>
      <event start="T1108-628" end="T351">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T352">sam blo je skeri, t@kr@t k je rojevala, </event>
      <event start="T352" end="T1111-569">to j tista ... </event>
      <event start="T1112-904" end="T354">Aoo, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T1114-371">hoč@š, d spojlam? </event>
      <event start="T1114-371" end="T1115-889">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1115-889" end="T355">Ne, skratka, </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T1118-739">pač na neki točki je nek tm en bejbi. </event>
      <event start="T1119-192" end="T356">In ta bejbi bi mogu bit ful prfekt, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T357">k je vampir al vatever, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1122-862">a n. </event>
      <event start="T1123-466" end="T358">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T359">amp@k so nardil lutko </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T360">in ta lutka je tko ful of-puting, </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T1127-688">tko ful je faking skeri. </event>
      <event start="T1128-311" end="T1129-395">Ful je bed. </event>
      <event start="T1129-395" end="T1130-496">Ful je bed. </event>
      <event start="T1130-496" end="T361">Pa tud Bela, </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T362">t@kr@t k je tko neki ful švohcena, </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T1133-244">a n. </event>
      <event start="T1133-244" end="T363">K je ful suha, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T364">vatever, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T1136-297">so isto lutko nardil ful of-puting. </event>
      <event start="T1136-297" end="T1140-09">Ampak je bl of-puting zato, k ... izgleda isto k igralka. </event>
      <event start="T1140-09" end="T365">[zvok] In sam tko </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1141-845">voa. </event>
      <event start="T1143-647" end="T1145-138">_@nkeni veli. </event>
      <event start="T1145-692" end="T1146-369">_@nken() </event>
      <event start="T1146-369" end="T1147-643">_@nkeni veli. </event>
      <event start="T1147-643" end="T1148-153">Mejkap. </event>
      <event start="T1148-153" end="T1149-981">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1149-981" end="T1151-172">Pa eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1161-328" end="T1163-134">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1163-941" end="T1165-271">Hanger Gejms. </event>
      <event start="T1165-271" end="T1165-703">Feral. </event>
      <event start="T1168-510" end="T1169-537">Igre lakote. </event>
      <event start="T1171-77" end="T1172-121">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1173-634" end="T1175-826">A je not tud Dž() Dž() Džoš Hačeršen? </event>
      <event start="T1178-978" end="T1179-655">Je dip. </event>
      <event start="T1179-938" end="T372">Dis ajm fortin </event>
      <event start="T372" end="T1181-396">end dis is dip. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1183-126" end="T1183-937">Fer. </event>
      <event start="T1186-593" end="T1189-393">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1189-393" end="T1190-604">Ne, ampak </event>
      <event start="T1190-604" end="T1192-371">te stvari so mene pušale tru. </event>
      <event start="T1192-371" end="T1193-755">Osnovna šola. </event>
      <event start="T1193-755" end="T374">Jz b(), </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T375">če jz če ne bi mela Herija Poterja, jz ne bi naredila osnovne šole, </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T1197-425">men je prov žov. </event>
      <event start="T1199-316" end="T1200-051">Emo. </event>
      <event start="T1200-637" end="T1203-02">[zvok] Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1203-02" end="T1204-438">Emo. </event>
      <event start="T1204-438" end="T376">K vedno sem tko: </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T377">"Dobr, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T378">pa sej nism nisem bla tok imo, k sem bla mejhna, </event>
      <event start="T378" end="T379">rajt?" </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T380">In pol grem gledat tko stare slike </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T381">in sem tko: </event>
      <event start="T381" end="T1211-11">"O, moj bog." </event>
      <event start="T1212-826" end="T383">No, its not. </event>
      <event start="T383" end="T1214-719">Its rili not. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1218-778" end="T1221-47">Ju ken tejk imo avt of mi? [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1221-47" end="T1222-101">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1222-101" end="T384">Ju ken tejk </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T385">ju ken tejk mi avej from imo </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T1229-435">end ju ken tejk [jezik] imo out of mi. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1229-925" end="T1231-536">To sim tetovirala ... </event>
      <event start="T1232-189" end="T1233-34">čez prsi. </event>
      <event start="T1233-34" end="T1236-926">[smeh] </event>
    </tier>
