      <event start="T217-133" end="T217-874">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T223-453" end="T226-456">To se vedno pol moraš pripraviti pol na na pet ur plus. </event>
      <event start="T228-28" end="T229-744">Ooo! </event>
      <event start="T229-744" end="T231-239">Nobenega? </event>
      <event start="T236-858" end="T238-04">Ona sta sama not sedela? </event>
      <event start="T238-718" end="T239-937">Ooo bad. </event>
      <event start="T245-306" end="T245-627">Uh! </event>
