      <event start="T281-959" end="T84">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T84" end="T282-742">okej. </event>
      <event start="T287-756" end="T289-244">On je tebe vprašal? </event>
      <event start="T289-244" end="T290-091">Dobro. </event>
      <event start="T295-154" end="T299-473">A pa to je za plačati za injekcije ... ali to ti krije z ...? </event>
      <event start="T300-974" end="T89">Okej okej. </event>
      <event start="T89" end="T90">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T90" end="T303-085">jaz to vem. </event>
      <event start="T305-162" end="T305-915">Nn! </event>
      <event start="T306-571" end="T93">Ooo </event>
      <event start="T93" end="T94">najebala, </event>
      <event start="T94" end="T309-311">najebala. </event>
      <event start="T311-963" end="T95">Ja oh, </event>
      <event start="T95" end="T96">itak, </event>
      <event start="T96" end="T313-884">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T315-44" end="T316-116">M? </event>
      <event start="T317-435" end="T99">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T99" end="T319-119">Jebote. </event>
      <event start="T321-199" end="T322-52">A prej te sploh ni na dotik? </event>
      <event start="T322-981" end="T323-534">Oh. </event>
      <event start="T323-534" end="T325-118">Bad. </event>
      <event start="T325-118" end="T100">Meni je to, </event>
      <event start="T100" end="T101">enkrat sem šla k te, v osnovno šolo k zobarici, </event>
      <event start="T101" end="T328-549">k isto. </event>
      <event start="T328-549" end="T329-759">Me najbolj me je zob bolel. </event>
      <event start="T329-759" end="T102">In sem šla k njej, </event>
      <event start="T102" end="T332-27">k je pač isto dežurna bila. </event>
      <event start="T332-27" end="T103">In eee ona tako pride tako: </event>
      <event start="T103" end="T104">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T104" end="T335-944">ti imaš gnoj pod zobom." </event>
      <event start="T335-944" end="T105">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T105" end="T106">"What do you ... </event>
      <event start="T106" end="T337-6">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T337-6" end="T339-388">what the fuck do you mean?" [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T339-388" end="T341-421">In ona meni zvrtala not luknjo. </event>
      <event start="T341-938" end="T342-586">V zob. </event>
      <event start="T342-876" end="T343-879">Da je šel gnoj ven. </event>
      <event start="T343-879" end="T344-837">Takat sem bila še ful majhna, </event>
      <event start="T344-837" end="T107">to ni bilo zdaj, </event>
      <event start="T107" end="T346-788">ampak da je šel gnoj ven. </event>
      <event start="T346-788" end="T348-985">In mene pač ona pusti najdlje cajta. </event>
      <event start="T348-985" end="T350-281">Pridem nazaj ... </event>
      <event start="T350-281" end="T108">ali ... ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T108" end="T109">ne vem, kako je že bilo, </event>
      <event start="T109" end="T353-453">skratka, spet sem rabila k njej. </event>
      <event start="T353-453" end="T110">In mi ga je ona eem </event>
      <event start="T110" end="T111">pač bila tako: </event>
      <event start="T111" end="T112">"Zdaj ga bova pa spulile," </event>
      <event start="T112" end="T357-322">k je pač bil mlečen. </event>
      <event start="T357-322" end="T113">Hvala bogu, </event>
      <event start="T113" end="T114">ampak bila tako: </event>
      <event start="T114" end="T359-344">"Zdaj ga bova spulile." </event>
      <event start="T359-344" end="T360-567">K m() pač ... mrtev je. </event>
      <event start="T361-072" end="T115">[zvok] In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T115" end="T362-368">"Okej." </event>
      <event start="T362-368" end="T116">Ona mi ga puli </event>
      <event start="T116" end="T364-063">in ne gre ven. </event>
      <event start="T364-063" end="T367-660">In se ji tip eee zdrobi v moji dlesni. </event>
      <event start="T367-660" end="T117">In ni mogla sv() celega sploh dati ven </event>
      <event start="T117" end="T118">in sem imela že tako, </event>
      <event start="T118" end="T119">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T119" end="T373-607">tri leta pol tako noter koščke. </event>
      <event start="T373-607" end="T375-732">Pač pa še z() pa še pa še zadaj je bilo, </event>
      <event start="T375-732" end="T377-471">k mi ni ful ccc cajta zrastel. </event>
      <event start="T377-471" end="T120">In naenkrat se samo zbudim, </event>
      <event start="T120" end="T379-194">samo tako: </event>
      <event start="T379-194" end="T121">"Hm, </event>
      <event start="T121" end="T122">ni več koščkov, </event>
      <event start="T122" end="T381-499">I'm done." </event>
      <event start="T381-499" end="T383-136">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T386-038" end="T386-391">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T387-004" end="T124">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T124" end="T388-258">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T389-955" end="T125">Najbolj trdi, </event>
      <event start="T125" end="T392-542">mi jih je iz cimra prinesla. </event>
      <event start="T392-853" end="T393-422">Najbolj trdi. </event>
      <event start="T396-656" end="T397-651">Jabolčni zih. </event>
      <event start="T398-313" end="T399-251">Ooh. </event>
      <event start="T401-724" end="T403-382">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T406-256" end="T406-695">Oh! </event>
      <event start="T408-912" end="T410-282">Jaz bi jokala. </event>
      <event start="T411-379" end="T412-146">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T414-576" end="T416-382">That's ... traumatic. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T416-382" end="T417-141">Koliko si bila stara? </event>
      <event start="T418-983" end="T132">Zobna miška. </event>
      <event start="T132" end="T421-842">Ja! [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T421-842" end="T133">Fak, </event>
      <event start="T133" end="T134">jaz sem, </event>
      <event start="T134" end="T425-449">jaz sem vedno tako pisala pisma zobni miški. </event>
      <event start="T425-449" end="T135">Mi smo imeli miško, </event>
      <event start="T135" end="T426-767">ne vilo. </event>
      <event start="T426-767" end="T428-489">Zo() zobna miška. </event>
      <event start="T428-489" end="T137">In sem, vedno sem jo tako najbolj spraševala vprašanja </event>
      <event start="T137" end="T434-774">in pol si prav samo tako predstavljam moja starša, k sta tako v sredi noči tam v cimru tako: </event>
      <event start="T434-774" end="T138">"Kaj naj ji odgovoriva, </event>
      <event start="T138" end="T437-338">kako naj ji to razloživa? </event>
      <event start="T437-338" end="T139">Ne vem, kaj, </event>
      <event start="T139" end="T439-4">ne vem, kaj." </event>
      <event start="T439-4" end="T140">In zadnjič mi tako mami kaže </event>
      <event start="T140" end="T442-816">in ima tako vse moje zobe. </event>
      <event start="T442-816" end="T443-761">Mi jih pokaže. </event>
      <event start="T443-761" end="T141">Vse, </event>
      <event start="T141" end="T142">no, </event>
      <event start="T142" end="T444-835">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T444-835" end="T446-35">veliko. </event>
      <event start="T446-35" end="T143">Oh! </event>
      <event start="T143" end="T447-758">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T447-758" end="T449-358">ampak enkrat sem jo vprašala. </event>
      <event start="T449-358" end="T451-399">Po moje je bila tudi moja. </event>
      <event start="T451-399" end="T144">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T144" end="T453-848">saj to je tako ful ime za miš. </event>
      <event start="T453-848" end="T145">Zobno miš, </event>
      <event start="T145" end="T454-924">I guess. </event>
      <event start="T455-504" end="T146">Ama bila sem tako: </event>
      <event start="T146" end="T147">"Mami, </event>
      <event start="T147" end="T458-773">zakaj imaš to spravljeno?" [glas] </event>
      <event start="T458-773" end="T459-634">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T464-405" end="T464-961">Ja. </event>
